title: The Kooks Discography (Updated)
description:
This is an updated version of the old Kooks Discography. 
This one contains the same as the old one plus Inside In/Inside Out Acoustic, Live at Maidstone and more. Its is also more organized and has album art (most of them created by me) for everything.
In total it contains:

Albums:

-Inside In/Inside Out (Normal and Acoustic)
-Konk (Konk, RAK, and iTunes Bonus Tracks)

Live:

-Ancienne Belgique
-Barfly
-Cologne
-iTunes Session
-London Calling
-Maidstone
-Parkpop
-Rock Am Ring
-Switzerland
-T In The Park
    and more

Other:

-All of the Singles (missing 1 or 2 songs though)
-Covers 
-The Kooks First Demo
    and more

But remember to support the band and buy the albums if you want The Kooks to be able to continue making great music.
